text: Flor-de-Lis are a folk music group from Lisbon, Portugal. They competed in the Eurovision Song Contest 2009 with the song Todas as ruas do amor where they finished 15th. ==Members== * Daniela Varela * Paulo Pereira * José Camacho * Jorge Marques * Ana Sofia Campeã * Rolando Amaral * Pedro Marques ==References== Category:2004 establishments in Europe Category:2000s establishments in Portugal Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants Category:Folk music groups Category:Musical groups established in 2004 Category:Portuguese musicians
